{"sn17.13-20:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 17.13–20 ","sn17.13-20:0.2":"2. Dutiyavagga ","sn17.13-20:0.3":"Suvannanikkhasuttadiatthaka ","sn17.13-20:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn17.13-20:1.2":"“Idhaham, bhikkhave, ekaccam puggalam evam cetasa ceto paricca pajanami: ","sn17.13-20:1.3":"‘na cayamayasma suvannanikkhassapi hetu …pe… ","sn17.13-20:1.4":"suvannanikkhasatassapi hetu … ","sn17.13-20:1.5":"singinikkhassapi hetu … ","sn17.13-20:1.6":"singinikkhasatassapi hetu … ","sn17.13-20:1.7":"pathaviyapi jatarupaparipuraya hetu … ","sn17.13-20:1.8":"amisakincikkhahetupi … ","sn17.13-20:1.9":"jivitahetupi … ","sn17.13-20:1.10":"janapadakalyaniyapi hetu sampajanamusa bhaseyya’ti. ","sn17.13-20:1.11":"Tamenam passami aparena samayena labhasakkarasilokena abhibhutam pariyadinnacittam sampajanamusa bhasantam. ","sn17.13-20:1.12":"Evam daruno kho, bhikkhave, labhasakkarasiloko …pe… ","sn17.13-20:1.13":"evanhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. ","sn17.13-20:1.14":"Dasamam. ","sn17.13-20:1.15":"Dutiyo vaggo. ","sn17.13-20:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn17.13-20:2.1":"Dve pati dve suvanna ca, ","sn17.13-20:2.2":"Singihi apare duve; ","sn17.13-20:2.3":"Pathavi kincikkhajivitam, ","sn17.13-20:2.4":"Janapadakalyaniya dasati. "}